http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/CM-VS-condole-death/article14004548.ece

Chief Minister Oommen Chandy and Leader of the Opposition V.S.Achuthanandan have condoled the death of Swami Sudheendra Theertha, spiritual head of the Gowda Saraswath Brahman community.Mr.Chandy, in his message on Sunday, described the Swami as one who lend more divinity and grace to the traditional Indian culture.His demise was a great loss to the country, Mr.Chandy said.The Swami, though a spiritual leader, had firmly opposed and took a strong stance against many superstitions, Mr.Achuthanandan said in his message.